Package ohos.agp.components.element

Class PixelMapElement

  • java.lang.Object
    • ohos.agp.components.element.Element
      • ohos.agp.components.element.PixelMapElement
  • Direct Known Subclasses:
    FlexElement

    public class PixelMapElement
extends Element
    Provides an Element object that wraps a PixelMap object.

    You can create a PixelMapElement object based on a PixelMap object.

    Since:
    1

      • setTileMode

        public void setTileMode​(Shader.TileMode horizontalMode,
                        Shader.TileMode verticalMode)
        Sets the horizontal and vertical repeat behavior for this PixelMapElement.

        To check the result of TileMode, make sure the size of the PixelMap is smaller than that of the PixelMapElement. The value can be any of the following: Shader.TileMode.CLAMP_TILEMODE: copies the edge color. Shader.TileMode.REPEAT_TILEMODE: repeats the image horizontally and vertically. Shader.TileMode.MIRROR_TILEMODE: repeats the image horizontally and vertically, alternating mirror images.

        Parameters:
        horizontalMode - Indicates the horizontal repeat mode for this PixelMapElement.
        verticalMode - Indicates the vertical repeat mode for this PixelMapElement.
        Since:
        7
        See Also:
        setHorizontalTileMode(ohos.agp.render.Shader.TileMode), setVerticalTileMode(ohos.agp.render.Shader.TileMode)

      • setHorizontalTileMode

        public void setHorizontalTileMode​(Shader.TileMode horizontalMode)
        Sets the horizontal repeat behavior for this PixelMapElement.

        To check the result of TileMode, make sure the size of the PixelMap is smaller than that of the PixelMapElement. The value can be any of the following: Shader.TileMode.CLAMP_TILEMODE: copies the edge color. Shader.TileMode.REPEAT_TILEMODE: repeats the image horizontally. Shader.TileMode.MIRROR_TILEMODE: repeats the image horizontally, alternating mirror images.

        Parameters:
        horizontalMode - Indicates the horizontal repeat mode for this PixelMapElement.
        Since:
        7
        See Also:
